Which clusters belong to which germ layers?

library(Seurat)
library(tidyverse)
library(RColorBrewer)

Load umap whole.

load("/Volumes/Bud_SSD/20210505-seurat/flox-integr-clust-5/flox-MES-clust-12/umap-by-cluster-flox-MES-clust-12.Robj")
head(germ.umap)
table(germ.umap$wildtype.whole)

    W1.2 W2.1.1.1 W2.1.1.2 W2.1.1.3 W2.1.2.1 W2.1.2.2 W2.1.2.3   W2.2.1   W2.2.2     W4.1     W4.2       W5 
    1303     1343      911      146      851      593      473      819      616      569      312      227

Set germ layers.

germ.umap$biopop.whole <- recode(germ.umap$wildtype.whole, 
                                                           "W1.2" = "NMP", 
                                                           "W2.1.1.1" = "MMP", 
                                                           "W2.1.1.2" = "PMP", 
                                                           "W2.1.1.3" = "PGC", 
                                                           "W2.1.2.1" = "SHF", 
                                                           "W2.1.2.2" = "TPM",
                                                         "W2.1.2.3" = "HPM", 
                                                           "W2.2.1" = "FHF2", 
                                                         "W2.2.2" = "FHF1", 
                                                           "W4.1" = "HMB", 
                                                           "W4.2" = "PE", 
                                                           "W5" = "PN")

germ.umap$biopop.whole <- factor(germ.umap$biopop.whole, levels = c("NMP", "MMP", "PMP", "PGC", "SHF", "TPM", "HPM", "FHF2", "FHF1", "HMB", "PE", "PN"))
save(germ.umap, file = "/Volumes/Bud_SSD/20210505-seurat/flox-integr-clust-5/flox-MES-clust-12/umap-by-bio-pop-flox-MES-clust-12.Robj")

Generate label umap.

umap.label <- germ.umap %>% group_by(biopop.whole) %>% summarize(umap.1 = median(umap.1), umap.2 = median(umap.2))

Generate cluster umap.

cluster.umap <- ggplot() +
geom_point(data = germ.umap, mapping = aes(x = umap.1, y = umap.2, color = biopop.whole), size = 0.1) +
geom_text(data = umap.label, mapping = aes(x = umap.1, y = umap.2, label = biopop.whole), size = 3.5) +
labs(title = "Mesoderm, Nipbl Flox/+", x = "UMAP 1", y = "UMAP 2", color = "Cell Type") +
guides(color = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 2.3))) +
theme_classic(base_size = 7) +
theme(axis.line = element_blank(), axis.ticks = element_blank(), axis.text = element_blank(), plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 7), legend.key.size = unit(7, "pt"))

cluster.umap

ggsave(plot = cluster.umap, filename = "/Volumes/Bud_SSD/20210505-seurat/flox-integr-clust-5/flox-MES-clust-12/umap-by-bio-pop-flox-MES-clust-12.png", device = "png", width = 6.5, height = 4.5, units = "in")
